#. type: Plain text
#: ../../calc.texi:9031
msgid ""
"Thus @samp{[0, 1; 1, 1]^n * [1, 1]} computes Fibonacci numbers @expr{n+1} "
"and @expr{n+2}.  Here's one program that does the job:"
