msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../../calc.texi:14277
msgid ""
"Accents like @code{\\tilde} and @code{\\bar} translate into function calls "
"internally (@samp{tilde(x)}, @samp{bar(x)}).  The @code{\\underline} "
