"@tindex diff The @kbd{b d} (@code{calc-diff}) [@code{diff}] command computes "
"the bitwise difference of two numbers; this is defined by @samp{diff(a,b) = "
"and(a,not(b))}, so that @samp{diff(2#1100, 2#1010) = 2#0100}."
msgstr ""

