"representing the remainder of the vector.  Thus the vector @samp{[a, b, c, "
"d] = cons(a, [b, c, d]) = rcons([a, b, c], d)}.  Also, @samp{head([a, b, c, "
"d]) = a}, @samp{tail([a, b, c, d]) = [b, c, d]}, @samp{rhead([a, b, c, d]) = "
