"a vector of the dimensions of a vector, matrix, or higher-order object.  For "
"example, @samp{mdims([[a,b,c],[d,e,f]])} returns @samp{[2, 3]} since its "
"argument is a @texline @math{2\\times3} @infoline 2x3 matrix."
