#: ../../calc.texi:29557
msgid ""
"The @kbd{g l} (@code{calc-graph-log-x}) and @kbd{g L} "
"(@code{calc-graph-log-y})  commands allow you to set either or both of the "
"axes of the graph to be logarithmic instead of linear."
