#. type: Plain text
#: ../../calc.texi:29567
msgid ""
"For 3D plots, @kbd{g C-t}, @kbd{g C-r}, and @kbd{g C-l} (those are letters "
"with the Control key held down) are the corresponding commands for the ``z'' "
"axis."
